This directory is an example for asset exporting.

The Main scene, `example.tscn`, contains some basic uses of resources.
When it is exported, *everything* in this directory, apart from this readme,
will be duplicated into the target addon location.

Any reference to a resource in the file
is modified to refer to the duplicated resource instead.

Note how the resource for "the apple" is *not* in this directory, it's already in addons.
When 'example.tscn' is exported, that addon image is *not* duplicated.